{"tid":811982,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"英國教育監管機構提議   大學必須為黑人學生提供更多學位","createTime":"2018-09-09T09:36:31.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-10T10:48:03.000Z","uid":141151,"like":4,"dislike":29,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"ae49f313526053a915fdbd75bda73db38375f0be","tid":811982,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T09:36:31.000Z","msg":"教育監管機構The Office for Students (OfS) 提議，大學必須為黑人學生提供更多學位，以包容該種族的貧窮背景。<br />\n<br />\n有英國網民對此表示：「在我讀大學的日子裏，大學只優先關心所有學生的學業成功與否，而不是膚色。」<br />\n<br />\n英國大學受政治正確教條侵害多年，「大愛包容」的信奉者想將大學變成「多元包容」的場所，以照顧「多元面貌」的學生。於是由過去看重學業，變成按種族設立名額。甚至進一步將標準「平民化」，少些貴族階級意識，多放水，為了強制令不同種族大學生成績扯平，結果連精英大學的學術質素也直線下降。<br />\n<br />\n世界萬物，上尊下卑，怎可能沒有高低之分？如果覺得自己不能入學是歧視而不高興，可以退學，離開所謂充滿仇恨和歧視的西方國家，回到親愛祖國升學生活，愈快愈好。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://mastodon.social/@sunandmoon/100695059484449870\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmastodon.social%2F%40sunandmoon%2F100695059484449870&d=SuDdN0eGUOeRjBjatkZNKU%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=1c2cd18f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://mastodon.social/@sunandmoon/100695059484449870</a><br />\n<br />\nUniversities must give more top degrees to black students, under new proposals by regulator<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.telegraph.co.uk/education/2018/09/06/universities-must-give-top-degrees-black-students-new-proposals/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.telegraph.co.uk%2Feducation%2F2018%2F09%2F06%2Funiversities-must-give-top-degrees-black-students-new-proposals%2F&d=SuDdN0eGUOeRjBjatkZNKU%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=9c879394\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.telegraph.co.uk/education/2018/09/06/universities-must-give-top-degrees-black-students-new-proposals/</a>"},{"pid":"d18f3123ba1f556b9d4e925f88845ab9c5136db3","tid":811982,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T09:40:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1d6665c0fad4635